<header class="post-header">
    <h1 class="u-m-0_25">HopeMob, the &#8216;Kickstarter for causes&#8217;, relaunches as a no-fee fundraising platform open to all</h1>
    <div class="post-byline u-m-1_5">
        <a data-event-category="Article" data-event-action="Author - Josh Ong" data-event-label="Profile" data-event-non-interaction="true" class="lazy post-authorPhoto" data-src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/795d67416e79afbcf84f2300a5ef2590?s=64&amp;d=blank&amp;r=g" data-src-hd="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/795d67416e79afbcf84f2300a5ef2590?s=128&amp;d=blank&amp;r=g" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180703221057/https://thenextweb.com/author/joshong/" title="Josh Ong"></a>

        <p>
            by <a class="post-authorName" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180703221057/https://thenextweb.com/author/joshong/" data-event-category="Article" data-event-action="Author - Josh Ong" data-event-label="Profile" data-event-non-interaction="true">Josh Ong</a>
            &mdash; <time datetime="2012-12-08T03:41:12+01:00" class="timeago"></time>
                        in <a class="post-section" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180703221057/https://thenextweb.com/insider/" data-event-category="Article" data-event-action="Category" data-event-label="Insider" data-event-non-interaction="true">Insider</a>
