		<h2 class="u-m-1"><a href="/web/20180703221057/https://thenextweb.com/latest/" data-event-category="Article" data-event-action="Latest News" data-event-label="Headline" data-event-non-interaction="true">Latest</a></h2>
		<ul class="u-row">
			<li class="u-col-xs-12 u-col-m-6 u-col-l-12">
	<div class="story story--small" data-event-category="Article" data-event-action="Latest News" data-event-label="Post" data-event-non-interaction="true">
		<a class="lazy story-image gtm-latestnews" data-src="https://cdn0.tnwcdn.com/wp-content/blogs.dir/1/files/2018/07/OnePlus-6-Red-3-of-6-96x96.jpg" data-srcset="https://cdn0.tnwcdn.com/wp-content/blogs.dir/1/files/2018/07/OnePlus-6-Red-3-of-6-96x96.jpg 96w, https://cdn0.tnwcdn.com/wp-content/blogs.dir/1/files/2018/07/OnePlus-6-Red-3-of-6-192x192.jpg 192w, https://cdn0.tnwcdn.com/wp-content/blogs.dir/1/files/2018/07/OnePlus-6-Red-3-of-6-550x550.jpg 550w, https://cdn0.tnwcdn.com/wp-content/blogs.dir/1/files/2018/07/OnePlus-6-Red-3-of-6-470x470.jpg 470w" sizes="(max-width: 96px) 100vw, 96px" width="96" height="96" data-event-category="Article" data-event-action="Latest News" data-event-label="1" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180703221057/https://thenextweb.com/insider/2018/07/03/the-oneplus-6-red-is-unsurprisingly-very-red/"></a>
						<span class="story-rank">1</span>
						<h4 class="story-title">
			<a data-event-category="Article" data-event-action="Latest News" data-event-label="1" class="gtm-latestnews" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180703221057/https://thenextweb.com/insider/2018/07/03/the-oneplus-6-red-is-unsurprisingly-very-red/">
				The OnePlus 6 Red is, unsurprisingly, very red			</a>
		</h4>
